episodes.title: Empire of Yoga
episodes.description: This is about how Kundalini Yoga and Yogi Bhajan are now seen accurately as a cult that harmed people in many ways, and they are still doing damage, though many of the victims don’t realize it when it’s happening. For more info see https://www.3hno.org/
